import React from 'react';
import styled from 'styled-components';
import UserInfo from './UserInfo';
import Summary from './Summary';
import Experiences from './Experiences';
import Skills from './Skills'
import Educations from './Educations'
import InfoCard from './InfoCard'

const Wrapper = styled.div`
  display: block;
  padding 24px;
`

export default () => (
  <Wrapper>
    <InfoCard title={'Personuppgifter'}>
      <UserInfo/>
    </InfoCard>
    <InfoCard title={'Sammanfattning av erfarenheter'}>
      <Summary/>
    </InfoCard>
    <InfoCard>
      <Experiences title={"Tidigare erfarenheter"}/>
    </InfoCard>
    <InfoCard>
      <Educations/>
    </InfoCard>
    <InfoCard title={'Kompetens'}>
      <Skills/>
    </InfoCard>
  </Wrapper>
)
